Preheat oven to 400Â°F. In a large bowl, combine @hot country-style bulk pork sausage{1%lb} (uncooked), @sharp Cheddar cheese{3 1/2%cups} (grated), and @Bisquick{2%cups}. Mix with your hands until well combined with no dry crumbs.

